# Most Important Concept

## Explanation Box

```java
TreeNode left;
```

does NOT store a number.

❌ Wrong:

```text
left = 5
```

✔ Correct:

```text
left = Reference to another TreeNode
```

Visual:

```text
Node
 ├── Value
 ├── Reference to Left Node
 └── Reference to Right Node
```

Example:

```text
          [10]
          /  \
         /    \
       [5]   [15]
```

Node 10 stores:

```text
val = 10

left  ---> Node 5

right ---> Node 15
```

